Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, you've become quite reliable lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:08.84,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:12.42,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,My sister also seems to trust Mei-senpai a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.80,3,host,0,0,0,,N-Natsumi does?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.58,3,host,0,0,0,,It certainly doesn't look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I feel like Mei-chan naturally leads the first and second years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and gives them a push forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Just as Kanon-senpai says, Mei-senpai takes the lead in bringing us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.68,3,host,0,0,0,,Well, that's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:35.06,3,host,0,0,0,,If I don't do it, everyone just does whatever they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:36.08,3,host,0,0,0,,so I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's impressive that you can act without hesitation in those moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:44.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd just leave the leadership to Chi-chan or Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:49.90,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Mei-senpai was also very dependable when we headed to Music World.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.14,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard about that from Margarete-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You really worked hard, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:58.56,3,host,0,0,0,,At the time, I was hoping I could be a bit more like Chisato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:00:59.73,3,host,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.66,3,host,0,0,0,,looking back now, I think I was being a little too tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.08,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I think that's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:11.83,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Seeing Mei-senpai work hard has the benefit of making Liella more positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:12.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I totally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It makes us feel like we can't afford to lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.43,3,host,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.48,3,host,0,0,0,,Kanon-senpai and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.88,3,host,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.20,3,host,0,0,0,,There's no way you seniors would lose to someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's not true, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You just said 'someone like me,' didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:33.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You have more power to move those around you than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:36.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And the kindness to support others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.41,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.44,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Margarete says it often as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.37,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I can't afford to lose to Mei-senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.01,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,She says.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.84,3,host,0,0,0,,I can definitely imagine her saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.42,3,host,0,0,0,,By the way, Tomari, your Margarete impression is spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.56,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Anyway, Mei-chan, you're the driving force of Liella,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,so we're counting on you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.52,3,host,0,0,0,,The driving force?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.36,3,host,0,0,0,,Well, that might be a bit of an exaggeration,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:07.20,3,host,0,0,0,,but I'm ready to fire up the engine anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.88,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:15.38,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,In that case, please fire up my sister's motivation for the next periodic exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.07,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.69,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Then fire up my passion for baking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.60,3,host,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.28,3,host,0,0,0,,I can't look after you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:43.12,4,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' High School Broadcasting Station: Liella's Tomo-Kano-Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.29,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm Date Sayuri, aka Sayurin, the voice of Shibuya Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm Sakakura Saki, aka Sakuchan, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,And I'm Yabushima Akane, aka Yabuchan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,the voice of Yoneme Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.08,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:06.43,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So, this time we're bringing you Tomo-Kano-Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Welcome to the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.35,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.57,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:25.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Today is March 24th, but March 28th is 'Sunny Pa Day',
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:30.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and it's the birthday of Hijirisawa Yuna-chan and Yoshitake-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.58,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Sunny Pa Day really is Sunny Pa Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's like destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just too incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:37.75,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's wonderful. Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.16,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Let's all celebrate when the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.37,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:42.93,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Comment: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And now, we've received an email just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's from Liella Name, Kabo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.16,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.61,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Congratulations on being chosen to perform at LuckyFes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.17,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:05.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ibaraki is the hometown of the Onitsuka sisters and also my own hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,so seeing Liella live there was a dream of mine. I almost screamed at work when I saw the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The venue, Hitachi Seaside Park, is a place where I have many memories of school trips,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:22.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and of having barbecues with my family and friends when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:27.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So, I'm very happy to be able to make new memories there with everyone in Liella.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:27.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:32.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward to having the best time with Liella again this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.68,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,So the email says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:40.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next is Liella Name, Takashi-san from Sendai. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your appearance at LuckyFes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.27,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since the festival is in Ibaraki, a place with deep ties to the series,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.39,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I think it will feel extra special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:57.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it's a summer festival, please whip the crowd into a frenzy with Liella's hot performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:57.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm also looking forward to seeing if you'll perform any classic summer songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,True. Oh, and if you have any goals for the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:09.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,or things you'd like to try at a summer fest, I'd be happy if you could let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.90,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,So the email says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Yes, Liella will be appearing at LuckyFes on Day 2, the 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.40,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We've been confirmed to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's in Ibaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really is the Onitsuka sisters' hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:37.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and we've always wanted to perform in Ibaraki someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:42.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,so I'm so glad it's coming true. And the other artists are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.19,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:44.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:45.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.89,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:51.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We'll do our best to show off Liella's power and not be outdone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We look forward to seeing you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's the middle of summer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,August 8th and 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Make sure to stay energized,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:05:59.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and come visit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:00.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Bring your sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:02.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Bring your sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Are we going to perform while holding sports drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:05.95,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, should we do that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,They might end up spraying everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Spraying everywhere, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.59,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Our bodies would be all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please come and see us, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We look forward to seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.62,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now then, everyone, please stay with us until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:28.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station Liella Let's Super Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.48,4,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station Liella
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.50,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This is the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Suggestion Box, where we introduce your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now then, everyone together... Ready, set, Suggestion Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,All right, let's introduce an email.
Comment: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Alright. This one is from Liella Name Miku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:01.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I attended the Kanagawa performance in person and watched the Aichi performance via stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:07.45,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Mei-chan's solo song, Sky Linker, started with a baton pass from the club president, Chisato-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.06,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.48,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,What was particularly striking was the part at the end of the chorus where you thrust your fist forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.15,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:18.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since that part happens a few times, I was moved to tears the first time I saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and from the second time on, I was thrusting my fist right along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.43,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was a performance where I felt Mei-chan's immense love, her kindness that embraces weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:29.76,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and a straightforward strength that encompasses her desire to protect everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.64,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.78,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Next is from Liella Name Baron Ojipan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:43.94,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Regarding Sky Linker, the claps where you bring both hands to your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and the side steps afterward, looked like a traditional Spanish dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,specifically flamenco.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Spain is often called the land of passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and I felt that the dance expressed Mei-chan's hidden inner passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The moment I first saw it, I thought, "Whoa, that's so cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And with that, ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's a Spanish farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,(Laughs) That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:09.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Alright, next is Liella Name Red-haired Kana. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:20.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Seeing Sky Linker on Day 1 of the Kanagawa performance was truly the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-chan's dance was so cool that I can't get it out of my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.64,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and it still leaves a strong impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The song and lyrics are great too, so I listen to it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.83,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'd love to see the dance for Sky Linker again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:32.84,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.98,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.65,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.21,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I want to hear more about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Sky Linker was seriously cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:41.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:52.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,At first, I thought the performance might involve a mic stand or just standing and hyping up the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:52.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't really imagine her dancing intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:56.90,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:02.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I kept wondering how it would turn out, but I never expected flamenco in the interlude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, it was a very valuable experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.69,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever have another chance to do flamenco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:16.54,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,When I first saw the video of Mei-chan's choreography,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "What kind of dance is this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan was doing a style of dance that none of us had ever done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:29.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,When I said, "Oh, this is amazing," and heard it was flamenco, I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:33.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "How do you even do that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it at all at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No way, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:42.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The core strength and the foundation of the dance were completely different
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,from anything I'd used before. I'm not an expert on dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but even so, it was so difficult that I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:50.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I practiced just that interlude part over and over at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:57.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But you were really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:08.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Since we all do our solo choreography sessions separately,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.02,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we don't know when others are practicing, and to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:17.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we don't even know if each other's songs involve dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So when I met up with the other members, I'd ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"Wait, are you dancing to Kanon-chan's song?"
Comment: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.32,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like, "How much dancing is there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were all having conversations like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:32.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but I happened to run into Yabu right after she finished learning the choreo for Mei-chan's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:38.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's when she whispered to me, "It turned out to be flamenco..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And I was like, "Wait, hold on. What do you mean?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was just so confused. Like, "Flamenco?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Yabu was saying earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:52.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I imagined her standing tall at a stand mic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,with a burning passion, but then I heard it was flamenco.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:02.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You don't really get many chances to see flamenco, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Liella probably wouldn't do it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,No, we wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All of us doing flamenco together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:12.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It must be hard when you don't know what the "right" way is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:18.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It looks difficult just watching, so doing it yourself must have been a huge challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's incredibly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:23.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But I saw how much she practiced, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, her moves were so sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right? She looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:34.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Miku-san said, the part where you thrust your fist forward felt so direct and very Mei-chan-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:31.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:42.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It didn't feel like just "choreography" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:40.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It felt like you were thrusting your fist out of pure emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:54.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I found myself getting really emotional during that part, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That part happens at the end of the first verse,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,the end of the second verse,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:03.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and then after the final chorus, the song ends with it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The movement is exactly the same every time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:13.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I could feel that the emotions behind it were different in the first, second, and final parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:20.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Depending on the performance, what I'm feeling in that moment changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,so I put all of my feelings into that fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really love the sound of the glass shattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That part is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:31.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:35.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It stands out even more during a live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:40.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really resonated, and the flames in the background...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,matched Mei-chan perfectly and looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:42.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And right after that, we had "Fantastic," so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.61,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:53.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were preparing, so I was watching Mei-chan's performance from the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:57.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Feeling her heat, the two of us were like, "Alright, let's do this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"Let's keep this momentum going!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It was really, really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.34,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It was so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:11.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Can I say something too? Kanon performs right before Mei-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.66,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and since there's a bit of time before Kanon's next appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:19.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was able to see Mei-chan right before she went on to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I saw her from backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And of course, it was the same before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:31.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,but I'd also run into Yabu right after her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:38.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,She always had this look of having given it her all with such passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,but at the same time, she never seemed fully satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She'd have this expression like, "What should I do better next time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's how Yabu always looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's like... how do I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:56.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She had her own sense of accomplishment from giving her all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but she always had this look on her face like, "I've still got a long way to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That just felt so much like Mei-chan to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,that I almost started crying while drinking my hot water alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's so Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.36,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,From our perspective, we're all thinking, "You were wonderful!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone feels that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but she's just... how do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Her own... what's the word?
Comment: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.76,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The wall was so high... no, no, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone feels that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:32.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is so ambitious and shares that same mindset,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:38.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,which is why I feel inspired to work harder myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I might not have felt that way if I were alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:47.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but seeing and feeling everyone's performances made me think, "Maybe I can go further,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:51.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,or "Maybe there's more I can do."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We really were inspiring each other with our solo songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:00.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I felt it too. We all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mutual inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was really happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:11.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though a solo song is for one person, I felt like I wasn't alone during that performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It felt like we were all building it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and the costumes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That "Girl Crush" look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I've never worn anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:28.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If you called it "street clothes," it's probably the closest to what I'd actually wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:33.51,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's simple and stylish enough that you wouldn't look out of place walking around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Some people might actually wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The fishnet tights were lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.38,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That was a first for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I've never worn fishnets in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Is it okay for people to see you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I just felt grateful for the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.83,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were practically worshipping you backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.19,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was honored to be worshipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:50.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and during the final show, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:59.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It wasn't part of the choreography, but your hair
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:04.34,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,got in your face. You brushed it away while looking forward or down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I can't quite remember which, but that gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,was caught perfectly by the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was just too good. Like, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'd definitely watch that on repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you, hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was seriously so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "Whoa."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.87,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-san doesn't even remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But it was so beautiful, I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:32.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:34.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You have to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Some people might already be talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Please try to remember it, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.10,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.38,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Moving on, this is from Liella Name: Hajiketa Kata Popcorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.58,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! 7th Live
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That was tough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All the 2nd and 3rd generation members were saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:18.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,the choreography was incredibly difficult. It's the kind of difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,that's hard for the audience to imagine. From the outside, it looks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:29.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,like a fun and light dance, but it was actually incredibly tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really was a struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It truly was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.98,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,When we first learned the moves, we all felt like our souls were about to leave our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:19:05.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We were all worried if we could actually sing and dance it at the same time, but as we practiced, we got in sync, and that anxiety turned into enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:19.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So on the day of the live, instead of being worried, I felt like I could enjoy that sense of unity with the audience. What about you?
Comment: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:18.92,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:18.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:24.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right. Ever since "High Motivation" was announced,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:35.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,many people said they were excited to see the live performance, so I felt a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:44.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I thought the choreography would be a bit simpler or sweeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But there's actually a lot of dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:50.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:20:07.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's a fun song, so I was worried I wouldn't be able to express that, but as the live date got closer, all the practice gave me confidence to just enjoy it on the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:57.50,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:18.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I wanted to show that the 23rd generation alone has the power to pull it off and entertain everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:31.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,In the end, I was able to have fun, but at first, I couldn't even think about that. I was just desperate. When we first tried singing and dancing at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:28.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:37.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We all said, "This is impossible! This is really bad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:48.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though there are fewer of us in the 23rd generation than the original 11, we couldn't even catch our breath. The formation is so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:55.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And the way they pick up the rhythm isn't just a simple 1-2-3-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:21:03.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The choreographer had us moving to even the tiniest sounds in the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really was something, but it turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, what part was especially difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:17.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,From the audience's perspective, as Saku just said, it looks like you're hitting every single beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:24.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But since we're just watching, we just end up thinking, "That looks like fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:25.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Which part was actually hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,With other songs, I can usually point to a specific part that was tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:38.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but with this one, every part is a little bit difficult, so it feels like it's hard the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:38.93,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's just... tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:46.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How should I put it? There are almost no scenes where you're just standing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,watching the other girls while it's not your part to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You're always doing one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:22:00.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We're constantly moving, and while the formations were hard, I was mostly just out of breath from moving so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.45,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:07.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I can say it now, but the choreography lessons were pretty intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:08.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:09.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:12.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone was crying while we were doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:13.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was a total mess, crying my eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really wondered what was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I thought, "Mei-chan would never cry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:20.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:28.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but seeing her cry made me cry even more. I don't even know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:27.71,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, I can say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:43.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone must have practiced so much at home, because when we met again, the quality was on a whole different level. I was so impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The lyrics even mention something about "having changed," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:51.82,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Hearing that now, I think that's what it was referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I wasn't there myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:58.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The song title is "High Motivation," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:22:59.79,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even during rehearsals, the 23rd generation would shout,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:08.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,"High Motivation!" to pump themselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seeing that, I just thought it was so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:18.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, you really need that kind of motivation to get through a song like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:22.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But during the actual performance, everyone looked so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:30.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and you were all smiling. It made me realize how much hard work must have gone into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Because everyone gave it their all,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,it turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.50,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,By the way, did you see Nako's impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.61,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I guess you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.55,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You should have her show you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:39.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:39.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Did you take a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:43.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, I didn't, but she's always mimicking the "High Motivation" choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:49.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so cute, so you should definitely have Nako show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:49.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's a very specific part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:52.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:53.47,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I wonder which part it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:58.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.40,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:03.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, we've talked quite a bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:06.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,it's still not enough, so we'll continue the discussion next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:07.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:10.90,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Anyway, thank you all for sending in so many emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:11.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:15.47,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now, let's introduce an email for our Lunchtime Request segment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:16.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This one is from a listener named Mizuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:19.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.96,0:24:21.10,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,'I'd like to request Sky Linker.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:28.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,My favorite part of this song is definitely right before the last chorus,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,the part where you sing, "I'll change it, I'll change it right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:35.98,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Mei-chan usually speaks in a low voice, but in this part, she hits a clear high note.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.98,0:24:40.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I absolutely love the gap and her soul-stirring vocals.'
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.12,Date Sayuri,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:43.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.72,0:24:46.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel the soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:59.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's a very passionate song, so please pay attention not just to the vocals, but to the music in the background as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.82,0:25:03.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yoneme Mei, "Sky Linker."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.16,0:25:10.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,You only notice the missing pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:18.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,because you know what the perfect shape looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:21.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:28.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'm far from a god who can end someone's hesitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.80,0:25:36.40,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,but I'll stay in the rain with you until we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:42.36,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,My wish is in the blue sky; take my hand and I'll lead you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:47.74,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything, yes, I'll block out all the uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.74,0:25:50.68,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:52.67,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:58.60,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, don't lose to this depressing world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.60,0:26:00.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Through
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:14.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,thousands of sunrises, I'll fly and leap toward our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:18.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,We've become what they call "comrades."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:29.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,When I pray for someone other than myself, I'll prove there's not a single cloud in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.04,0:26:35.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Dive into the blue sky; if you hold my hand, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:37.79,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything—what's wrong with being weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.24,0:26:44.16,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,If you want to cry, let's cry and scream; I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:46.18,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:50.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, I'll accept any version of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:51.88,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:20.92,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,It's already cracked, but I'll show you I can catch it all without breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:32.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,If you want a tough vessel, if you want a clear "now," I'll change it for you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.80,0:27:34.04,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,In that blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.68,0:27:37.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,if we look up, the brilliant blue will lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:39.31,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.88,0:27:42.56,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything, I'll block out the uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:45.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.16,0:27:51.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll support you; you have a place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:53.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Don't you ever lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Friendship Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.56,0:28:13.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:19.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Announcements from Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.24,0:28:21.42,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Here is the music news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:23.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,On Wednesday, July 8th, the release of the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.64,0:28:27.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Liella! no Musubu Project" mini-album has been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:34.82,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We will be releasing five versions: the Original, Photo, Team Kodomo, Team Sports, and Team Midori editions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.82,0:28:41.94,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The Original, Team Kodomo, Team Sports, and Team Midori editions will feature new illustrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.94,0:28:45.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,while the Photo Edition will feature new photos of the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.26,0:28:52.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's expected to include 4 songs in total, including one new group song, plus off-vocal versions for a total of 8 tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:56.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,As a first-press bonus, the Original, Team Kodomo,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.76,0:29:00.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Team Sports, and Team Midori editions will include member stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The Photo Edition will include a Purikura-style sticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.56,0:29:08.10,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,All versions will also include an advance lottery application ticket for the "Love Live! Series 15th Anniversary Love Live! Fes"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.10,0:29:11.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and "Love Live! Superstar!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.36,0:29:14.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,As a bundle purchase bonus, we'll be giving away a Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,sticker book.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:17.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:19.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,To celebrate the release of the Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:24.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,no Musubu Project mini-album, a handover event has been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.72,0:29:29.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The dates are Friday, October 2nd, and Friday, October 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Those who pre-order or purchase the Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:38.40,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,no Musubu Project mini-album at participating stores will be invited to the handover event via lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:45.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The performers differ for each date, so please check the application requirements before applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:49.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please check the Love Live! Superstar!! official website for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.68,0:29:53.83,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,An announcement from the Love Live! Series Official Card Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The Start Deck "Love Live! Superstar!!",
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:30:02.78,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,featuring only Liella! members and songs, will be released on Saturday, May 30th.
Comment: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:08.68,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:08.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This product will include a special rarity, "Secret Serial," featuring a serial number.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:13.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Each numbered card is a super-luxurious, one-of-a-kind item.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.44,0:30:24.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The Start Deck has everything you need to play Loveca right away, so if you haven't tried it yet, please pick one up and start playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.36,0:30:32.36,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We'll be posting the latest updates on the official Love Live! website and X, so stay tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:34.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now for some appearance information.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.22,0:30:35.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Starting April 1st,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:36.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Season 2 of Liella!'s ChuChu Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.68,0:30:38.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,will begin on Nippon TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.16,0:30:43.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Haishin 3-go will continue as the program MC from Season 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:48.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Catch-up streaming will be available on TVer and Nittele TADA after the terrestrial broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.86,0:30:50.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:54.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,To celebrate the broadcast, Love Live! Superstar!! Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:55.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,no ChuChu Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:31:02.34,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,2026 will be held at LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY on August 1st and 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.34,0:31:10.02,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The official second lottery is currently open on Ticket Pia until 11:59 PM on Sunday, April 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.02,0:31:11.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please check this out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.44,0:31:16.74,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,For details on all the information shared today, please check the official Love Live! Superstar!! Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:21.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,X account or the official Love Live! Superstar!! website.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:23.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's all for the announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.16,0:31:35.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yu-Yu-Yu Lunchtime Broadcasting Station Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Radio. It's almost time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Here is the information for our upcoming broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:51.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,For the 266th episode on Tuesday, March 31st, we'll continue to have Yabushima Akane (voice of Yoneme Mei) as our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:32:02.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And for the 267th episode on Tuesday, April 7th, we'll welcome Okuma Wakana (voice of Shiki Wakana) as a guest for a "Toma-Kano-Shiki" episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.22,0:32:04.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're looking forward to your messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.44,0:32:07.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So, how did you enjoy today's broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.80,0:32:08.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.44,0:32:10.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:11.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ding, ding, ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:13.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What? Is it always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.89,0:32:15.39,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ding, ding, ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:19.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:19.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no, oh no, oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.96,0:32:21.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Saku... Sakura, you really surprised me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.84,0:32:23.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to join in on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:26.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, "When did Sakura become like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:27.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:33.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of a comeback, so I thought I'd just join in with one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:32.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:34.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.88,0:32:37.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabushima was looking so confused just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Saku... Sakura got someone worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:41.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Being worried about is the most embarrassing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:44.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, how was it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.26,0:32:49.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, I got to share my thoughts in great detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.34,0:32:51.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Or rather, I got to talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:52.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:53.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.92,0:32:55.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone wanted to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:32:57.99,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We'll talk more next week too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.99,0:32:58.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.56,0:33:02.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wonder how long we can keep talking about the 7th Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:05.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We're planning for about three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.62,0:33:06.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Roughly, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:09.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We'll keep going until we've covered every song.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.92,0:33:08.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, then we'll do every single song.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.52,0:33:10.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We won't be able to do the unit lives then!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.56,0:33:12.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.26,0:33:12.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We'll run over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.84,0:33:13.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We'll run over, we'll run over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.60,0:33:19.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's all for this episode of Love Live! Superstar!! Yu-Yu-Yu Lunchtime Broadcasting Station Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:20.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:22.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your hosts were Date Sayuri (voice of Shibuya Kanon),
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.36,0:33:24.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Sakakura Sakura (voice of Onitsuka Sumire),
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:26.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and Yabushima Akane (voice of Yoneme Mei).
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:36.64,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,In the breathtaking sunset, I heard a "see you later"...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:39.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,The breeze and you...
